Everyday Essentials and Amazon=E2=80=99s First Party Retail Business
------------------------------------------------------------

What is particularly notable to me is just how profitable the North America=
n retail business has become:

Amazon=E2=80=99s logistics network was also dramatically overbuilt during C=
OVID, and the combination of growing into and rationalizing that capacity w=
as a big drag on earnings; now, though, revenue growth has significantly ex=
ceeded expenses growth for nearly two years, leading to big profits. Notice=
, though, that their growth rates are re-converging. It will be interesting=
 to see if Amazon can maintain a gap in growth rates; even if they keep the=
m even, though, the gap that was built-up over the last two years should co=
ntinue to be a very profitable one.

